snippet.title: Hundred Acre Wood - Official Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description:
See gameplay and watch as Winnie-the-Pooh goes on the hunt in this trailer for Hundred Acre Wood, an upcoming Lovecraftian horror survival game. Hundred Acre Wood will be available on PC.

Explore and survive a twisted Hundred Acre Wood while being hunted by an old childhood friend, Winnie-the-Pooh. Rescue Christopher Robin with the help of Eldritch Beasts that were once familiar faces. Discover what took place and has changed a once beautiful land into something dark and dangerous.

#IGN #Gaming
